::Zardus/DevilDuer::

Zardus looks at Feline's body as she bends to give him his drink, DevilDuer 
looking at her butt. DevilDuer was still recovering from her calling him 
handsome, a bit of jealousy going through him from the fact that Feline was 
bending over in front of Zardus.

Zardus' eyes follow Feline back to her seat, an idea forming in his mind. 
Yess.. He had the perfect mission for her and the other new recruit. Zardus 
silently commands his internal computer to display the location of 
Skulletron, reveiwing over what happened in the training room over the last 
few cycles. He taps his comm-link.

"Bloodystrike," he says into it, his tone having its ussual deadly flavor, 
"Please bring the new recruit, I might have a mission for him."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Bloodystrike takes a few steps back from Skulletron as he recieves Zardus' 
transmission, putting away his weapons.

"Ok, let's go to Zardus," he says to Skulletron, "He wants to see you."
